se,"excerpt":"Shakal ibn Humayd reported: I came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me to seek refuge that by it I may seek refuge.\u201d The Prophet took me by the hand and he said, \u201cSay: O Allah, I seek refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41864,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/03\/21\/refuge-harm-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":34519,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from harming another Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Rashid reported: I came to Abdullah ibn Amr, and I said, \u201cNarrate to me what you have heard from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Abdullah set out a scroll, and he said, \u201cThis is what the Messenger of Allah has written for me.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2575,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/29\/seek-refuge-after-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":34519,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for refuge at the end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you finishes his testimony at the end of prayer, let him seek refuge in Allah from four trials, saying: O Allah, I seek refuge in You from the punishment of Hell, from the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15494,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dua-traveling-at-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":34519,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for traveling at night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: Whenever the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out on a journey, he would say by nightfall, \u201cO earth, my Lord and your Lord is Allah. I seek refuge in Him from your evil, from the evil you contain, from the evil created\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23351,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/01\/seeks-refuge-evil-neighbor\/","url_meta":{"origin":34519,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Refuge: The Prophet seeks refuge from evil moments","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 1, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from an evil day, from an evil night, from an evil moment, from an evil companion, and from an evil neighbor in the final abode.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/28\/dua-refuge-bad-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":34519,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I seek refuge in Allah from bad character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutbah ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from evil character traits, evil deeds, and evil desires.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3591 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0642\u0637\u0628\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34519","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34519"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34519\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.